{"tid":140423,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人返工會覺得好緊張","createTime":"2017-03-02T07:25:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T06:21:05.000Z","uid":88637,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b521b655dc65bd5c7d0a6311e29981de3b855ca","tid":140423,"uid":88637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:25:25.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返臨時工一個月都係一兩日就走果啲<br />\n有咩方法解決<br />\n開始唔敢搵工<br />\n費事又做唔長<br />\n<br />\n係果種返左幾日其實冇乜大問題 <br />\n工作做得黎<br />\n但一諗到下星期再黎就會好depress同緊張<br />\n晚晚惡夢 喊到肺都甩<br />\n放假都諗住<br />\n係可以點捱過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：失業九個月"},{"pid":"11cd13e2d0c0d8b7e6ca83e2ef9461f10071eeb8","tid":140423,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:27:47.000Z","msg":"主要係怕人"},{"pid":"33a2c8425c1e09a2cebee5d32f1116db49bb83be","tid":140423,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:31:16.000Z","msg":"第一日萬寧，on99咁唔知自己做過乜，失業5個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ebea60db21bcafee368d3297e2c0bc97178b03b","tid":140423,"uid":88637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:32:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>主要係怕人</blockquote><br />\n咁就易搞<br />\n搵啲唔洗對人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9826f5b399ca696c01b49d1244441543f3a956","tid":140423,"uid":88190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":