ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T10:05:12.000Z","msg":"係咪工作上 好多ad hoc?<br />\n<br />\n如果機械式，應該好快慣"},{"pid":"8686085004e251fe7e072d170b875fdd99a4a774","tid":140423,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T10:33:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>主要係怕人</blockquote><br />\n咁就易搞<br />\n搵啲唔洗對人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n怕對同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f14e4a225492ecb2dc5bff4cec5cab695202f43","tid":140423,"uid":88637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T10:40:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪工作上 好多ad hoc?<br />\n<br />\n如果機械式，應該好快慣</blockquote><br />\n基本上係 每日都唔知返去要做咩 一星期返兩三日 日日都好趕 所以先請我呢啲人返<br />\n幫人唔到仲想走 好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11089077b48eb83f24fb747d47afd49aea6eaba8","tid":140423,"uid":88637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T11:10:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>主要係怕人</blockquote><br />\n咁就易搞<br />\n搵啲唔洗對人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n怕對同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n企唔企得？"},{"pid":"299851d5e7f827e83ba2e399d41acc9b26bb675b","tid":140423,"uid":88637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T11:13:26.000Z","msg":"維持好多年啦 真係好想搵個岀口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c21a4cae7ba97aa795e31f6aa1f59e6972c3052","tid":140423,"uid":20554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,