ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T13:58:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我，可能係責任心太大+份人太易緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n輕鬆唔到咁番工，眼見d mk仔同事hea下hea下一日好熟習番工好似來玩咁<br />\n其實好葡萄，好想做到佢地既心態，因為佢地咁公司唔炒就得過且過，往往先做得長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都自問一開工就入狀態"},{"pid":"b503708925c14c2930130597688b0559c974ac2b","tid":140423,"uid":88637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:00:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主可講下工作類型嗎？</blockquote><br />\n乜工都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近排係趕住做文件 要交政府 再下放approval 唔係返左好多日 斷斷續續"},{"pid":"d26c3f7ab465facaf603992f79db8c342929e90d","tid":140423,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:51:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有焦慮症<br />\n返工勁辛苦</blockquote><br />\n點克服？</blockquote><br />\n死頂"},{"pid":"76f26042a442f918ef8e84af2717db891c48bcfc","tid":140423,"uid":8650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:55:31.000Z","msg":"屌我都會，勁想逃避，唯有逼自己頂硬上"},{"pid":"27c03195a5f8cf12fbb075be5e1b957e773b522a","tid":140423,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:55:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有焦慮症<br />\n返工勁辛苦</blockquote><br />\n點克服？</blockquote><br />\n死頂</blockquote><br />\n一樣<br />\n日日都死頂"},{"pid":"eb69bbb25e75eb2e4508ef654af6905bced4365c","tid":140423,"uid":88371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T05:06:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有焦慮症<br />\n返工勁辛苦</blockquote><br />\n點克服？</blockquote><br />\n死頂</blockquote><br />\n一樣<br />\n日日都死頂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前讀U 緊張到搭車會作嘔頭暈眼花<br />\n死頂果種感覺真係試過既人先知有幾辛苦<br />\n而家番hea工 已經完全冇問題<br />\n可以交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d28e7a71e4c262da6789c68c47b78f7f87bff05","tid":140423,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T05:20:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有焦慮症<br />\n返工勁辛苦</blockquote><br />\n點克服？</blockquote><br />\n死頂</blockquote><br />\n一樣<br />\n日日都死頂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前讀U 緊張到搭車會作嘔頭暈眼花<br />\n死頂果種感覺真係試過既人先知有幾辛苦<br />\n而家番hea工 已經完全冇問題<br />\n可以交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n近排上司冇派野俾我做<br />\n我成日驚係自己太廢，依加好擔心成世係低層職，中年失業"},{"pid":"255bca8b71c0c9393d17ab21fe86d5ca80ab78ba","tid":140423,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T05:29:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有焦慮症<br />\n返工勁辛苦</blockquote><br />\n點克服？</blockquote><br />\n死頂</blockquote><br />\n一樣<br />\n日日都死頂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前讀U 緊張到搭車會作嘔頭暈眼花<br />\n死頂果種感覺真係試過既人先知有幾辛苦<br />\n而家番hea工 已經完全冇問題<br />\n可以交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有病都無你咁誇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係一入公司就周身唔聚財<br />\n好緊張好怕個地方"},{"pid":"bacac82ee8bca593bf39662b7b3a4b3e0f718925","tid":140423,"uid":65649,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T05:37:12.000Z","msg":"首先份份工頭2個月都係咁，返去冇野做又驚比人話懶冇用，有野做又驚做唔黎趕唔切。<br />\n<br />\n我開頭都會成日轉工，到咁上下突然諗通左一樣野<br />\n<br />\n只要我盡左力做，佢唔撚滿意最多都係炒9我遮，佢唔會殺左我架，點解我要咁驚呢?<br />\n<br />\n至此之後本住你夠疆就炒9我呢個心態<br />\n<br />\n做野放左，決斷力上升，試用期後我仲扭屎忽花迫佢加人工 (都係個句，唔鍾意咪炒9我)<br />\n<br />\n最後佢咪又係比我想要既人工我，自己又開心左<br />\n<br />\n記住point好重要，第一係你真心努力過，盡力做好份工，唔好怨天怨地冇人幫，盡左力自己都心安理得<br />\n<br />\n第二就係冇左呢份工係唔會死，唔好迫到自己痴左線，呢到d人同工種唔夾唔代表第二到你都唔岩，個個都有長處<br />\n<br />\n慢慢搵下個平衡點啦，加油"},{"pid":"885e18ca9bf75284281ad6006578e9db044e6eac","tid":140423,"uid":88637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:38:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有焦慮症<br />\n返工勁辛苦</blockquote><br />\n點克服？</blockquote><br />\n死頂</blockquote><br />\n一樣<br />\n日日都死頂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前讀U 緊張到搭車會作嘔頭暈眼花<br />\n死頂果種感覺真係試過既人先知有幾辛苦<br />\n而家番hea工 已經完全冇問題<br />\n可以交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有病都無你咁誇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係一入公司就周身唔聚財<br />\n好緊張好怕個地方</blockquote><br />\n搭車會喊 經常性坐最尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840261dae99c241e2d31b957fa9ad8130696d494","tid":140423,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:42:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有焦慮症<br />\n返工勁辛苦</blockquote><br />\n點克服？</blockquote><br />\n死頂</blockquote><br />\n一樣<br />\n日日都死頂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前讀U 緊張到搭車會作嘔頭暈眼花<br />\n死頂果種感覺真係試過既人先知有幾辛苦<br />\n而家番hea工 已經完全冇問題<br />\n可以交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有病都無你咁誇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係一入公司就周身唔聚財<br />\n好緊張好怕個地方</blockquote><br />\n搭車會喊 經常性坐最尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n轉左工已經無咩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2027e2d6d3672dad8d595b2027199f7e7949eb","tid":140423,"uid":86403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:46:25.000Z","msg":"same here<br />\n<br />\n對自己無信心,搵D自已應付到,慢慢增加番自信先"},{"pid":"111e07adbba0b67a7c8fce33a9388b4ad742b403","tid":140423,"uid":88190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:10:04.000Z","msg":"之前都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 讀U嗰陣返pt驚到死<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明超級輕鬆都好驚會做錯 手都震埋<br />\n都要慢慢搵到自己最掂最上手嗰範<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開始覺得自己都做到嘢<br />\n樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoj