br />\n死頂</blockquote><br />\n一樣<br />\n日日都死頂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前讀U 緊張到搭車會作嘔頭暈眼花<br />\n死頂果種感覺真係試過既人先知有幾辛苦<br />\n而家番hea工 已經完全冇問題<br />\n可以交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有病都無你咁誇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係一入公司就周身唔聚財<br />\n好緊張好怕個地方</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nI mean 係真係最辛苦既時候<br />\n咁緊係唔係100%時間咁誇張<br />\n唔知點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一半時候係冇乜野 緊張同心跳快少少<br />\n但有時候無啦啦諗到某d野令自己驚到一個點<br />\n就會好辛苦<br />\nsor 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n緊張到大部份時間都喊緊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一諗到呢世人都係咁既情緒就想死左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"931e08308500ef4b5d174024835ab049e11c476e","tid":140423,"uid":4010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:10:42.000Z","msg":"頭幾日返工緊張到仆街 成個人震哂郁唔到"},{"pid":"c2529d96f1e4c29c9e53a205bd53d2d86db18b3d","tid":140423,"uid":85011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T11:22:27.000Z","msg":"有病睇醫生"},{"pid":"feef65f358a874eeaa054005f892e0837c3b67d5","tid":140423,"uid":88637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:56:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有病睇醫生</blockquote><br />\n睇完先發現冇病咁只可以一生一世屌自己廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但做唔到啲咩<br />\n個情緒一到好難頂<br />\n會想即時了斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b422230bec5253927d3b278bd2a16ebb41a1532a","tid":140423,"uid":88371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:08:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有病睇醫生</blockquote><br />\n睇完先發現冇病咁只可以一生一世屌自己廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但做唔到啲咩<br />\n個情緒一到好難頂<br />\n會想即時了斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主喊既意思係 眼角流小小眼淚<br />\n定係啜泣果隻喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係你緊張會變到好情緒化?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86625925e4740d5599d6cbec165b437117a13738","tid":140423,"uid":54593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:30:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有焦慮症<br />\n返工勁辛苦</blockquote><br />\n點克服？</blockquote><br />\n死頂</blockquote><br />\n一樣<br />\n日日都死頂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前讀U 緊張到搭車會作嘔頭暈眼花<br />\n死頂果種感覺真係試過既人先知有幾辛苦<br />\n而家番hea工 已經完全冇問題<br />\n可以交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我緊張都會想作嘔 勁辛苦<br />\n返新工第一日係完全無乜胃口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7953dccadb7032789fc80d0dbf6803f7277905e","tid":140423,"uid":88637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T07:57:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有病睇醫生</blockquote><br />\n睇完先發現冇病咁只可以一生一世屌自己廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但做唔到啲咩<br />\n個情緒一到好難頂<br />\n會想即時了斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主喊既意思係 眼角流小小眼淚<br />\n定係啜泣果隻喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係你緊張會變到好情緒化?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係屋企喊到會嗌岀黎果種<br />\n係街係車戴住個口罩合埋眼由得佢不停流<br />\n盡量唔比人發現 <br />\n但好搞笑 係返工日果朝早唔會 仲識扮工！既<br />\n一放工放假就會黎料 所以會覺得頂唔順想quit job <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔係覺得返工攰 係要應付情緒好攰<br />\n有冇人可以教我克服佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：返散工都係咁 點敢返長工"},{"pid":"b54430bab6c678e6bb6bdcae6c03d9ff87beb0c5","tid":140423,"uid":88637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T07:58:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有焦慮症<br />\n返工勁辛苦</blockquote><br />\n點克服？</blockquote><br />\n死頂</blockquote><br />\n一樣<br />\n日日都死頂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前讀U 緊張到搭車會作嘔頭暈眼花<br />\n死頂果種感覺真係試過既人先知有幾辛苦<br />\n而家番hea工 已經完全冇問題<br />\n可以交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我緊張都會想作嘔 勁辛苦<br />\n返新工第一日係完全無乜胃口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你呢種我覺得都正常 第一日既緊張我逼自己當係日常 但困擾既係之後日復日都係咁"}]}